# Apex AI — Comprehensive Project Report
### AI-Powered Stock Market Prediction & Trading Signal Platform
> **Version:** 2.0 (Multi-Modal TFT Architecture) · **Updated:** March 2026
> **Team:** Sai Narendra Ghodke *(Lead AI Architect)* · Siddhartha Vijay Bhosale *(Data Scientist)* · Sunraj Shetty *(Frontend Engineer)*

---

## 1. Project Overview

**Apex AI** is a professional-grade, research-quality stock market analysis and prediction platform. It combines deep learning, multi-modal feature engineering, natural language sentiment analysis, and rigorous signal gatekeeping to surface high-conviction **BUY / SELL / HOLD** signals for US and Indian equities.

The system is designed to overcome a fundamental flaw in most retail AI trading tools: classic sequential (LSTM/GRU) models suffer from **lag** (chasing the trend) and **noise overfitting** (reacting to short-term spikes). Apex AI's V2 pivot to **Temporal Fusion Transformers (TFT)** with multi-modal inputs and probabilistic forecasting addresses these weaknesses directly.

---

## 2. Product Requirements Document (PRD)

### 2.1 Problem Statement

| Problem | Impact |
|---------|--------|
| LSTM/GRU "lag" — model chases trends instead of anticipating them | Low directional accuracy (<55%) |
| Noise overfitting — model reacts to irrelevant short-term spikes | False signals / poor risk-adjusted returns |
| Single-modality — only price data, no macro or sentiment context | Misses regime changes |
| Point predictions — no uncertainty quantification | Cannot size positions appropriately |

### 2.2 Target Audience

- **Retail Traders** — Seeking AI-derived alpha signals beyond simple moving averages
- **Institutional Analysts** — Needing probabilistic quantile forecast ranges
- **Quant Developers** — Looking for noise-denoised, stationary feature pipelines

### 2.3 Key Features (V2)

| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Multi-Modal Inputs** | Price + Technical Indicators + Macro (VIX, Bond Yields, DXY) + Sector metadata |
| **Attention-Based Forecasting** | Temporal Fusion Transformer (TFT) with self-attention to weigh historical relevance |
| **Probabilistic Forecast Cones** | Quantile outputs at P10 / P50 / P90 percentiles (7-day, 14-day, 30-day horizons) |
| **Signal Gatekeeping** | 3-gate confidence vetting before any BUY/SELL signal is emitted |
| **Explainable AI (XAI)** | SHAP/LIME plots: *"Why 60% Bullish? → RSI recovery + VIX declining"* |
| **FinBERT Sentiment** | Financial-domain BERT (`ProsusAI/finbert`) for news headline scoring |
| **Scenario Simulation** | Interactive "What-If" sliders for hypothetical market testing |
| **Market Screener** | Parallel S&P 500 scan with threaded TFT inference, ranked by confidence |
| **Smart Alerts** | Celery Beat tasks that push Telegram & Email alerts every 4 hours |
| **Paper Trading** | Simulated trade execution with SQLite-backed journal |

### 2.4 Development Roadmap

```
Phase 1 ✅  COMPLETED    Core LSTM + Basic Indicators + Streamlit UI
Phase 2 🔄  IN PROGRESS  Multi-Modal TFT, Macro Features (VIX/DXY), Wavelet Denoising
Phase 3 📋  PLANNED      Live Brokerage API + Multi-Horizon Portfolio Optimization
```

