## 4. Feature Engineering Pipeline

**File:** [utils/features.py](file:///d:/AI-Stock-market-prediction-master/AI-Stock-market-prediction-master/utils/features.py) — [build_all_features()](file:///d:/AI-Stock-market-prediction-master/AI-Stock-market-prediction-master/utils/features.py#330-408) orchestrates 4 stages:

### 4.1 Feature Types

Features are categorized by what the TFT network "knows" at inference time:

| Type | Description | Examples |
|------|-------------|---------|
| **UNKNOWN** | Time-varying, NOT known in advance | RSI, MACD, ATR, VIX, OBV, Stochastic, Bollinger Bands, all lags |
| **KNOWN_FUTURE** | Time-varying, deterministic at inference | Day-of-week, Month, Quarter, Month-end, Earnings date proximity |
| **STATIC** | Constant per ticker/entity | Sector, Industry, log(Market Cap), Beta |

### 4.2 Technical Indicators (15 columns)

| Indicator | Columns Generated | Window |
|-----------|------------------|--------|
| RSI | `RSI_14` | 14 |
| MACD | `MACD_12_26_9`, `MACDh_12_26_9`, `MACDs_12_26_9` | 12/26/9 |
| Bollinger Bands | `BBL_20_2`, `BBM_20_2`, `BBU_20_2`, `BBB_20_2` | 20, 2σ |
| ATR | `ATR_14` | 14 |
| OBV | `OBV` | — |
| Stochastic | `STOCHk_14_3_3`, `STOCHd_14_3_3` | 14/3 |

### 4.3 Lagged & Rolling Features

- Lagged copies of RSI, MACD, ATR at `lag = [1, 3, 5]` days
- `RSI_14_rolling_mean_5` — 5-day rolling RSI average
- `Volume_ratio` — today's volume / 20-day MA volume

### 4.4 Time / Calendar Features

- `day_of_week`, `month`, `quarter`, `is_month_end`, `is_quarter_end`, `days_to_earnings`

### 4.5 Macro & Denoised Features

- **VIX** (market fear index), **SP500**, **NSEI** (Nifty index)
- `Close_denoised` — Wavelet DWT denoised price (removes HF noise)
- `Close_fracdiff` — Fractionally differentiated price (maintains memory while ensuring stationarity)

