## 10. Alert System ([alerts.py](file:///d:/AI-Stock-market-prediction-master/AI-Stock-market-prediction-master/alerts.py))

Apex AI delivers actionable alerts automatically every **4 hours** via Celery Beat:

### 10.1 Delivery Channels

| Channel | Implementation |
|---------|---------------|
| **Telegram** | `python-telegram-bot ≥ 20` async bot, Markdown-formatted message |
| **Email** | `smtplib.SMTP_SSL`, dark-themed HTML template with P10/P50/P90, feature importance bars |

### 10.2 Alert Message Content
- Signal badge (🟢 BUY / 🔴 SELL / 🟡 HOLD) + Confidence score
- 14-day P10 / P50 / P90 price forecast table
- Risk note based on cone width
- Narrative signal rationale (SHAP explanation)
- Feature importance bar chart (email only)
- Direct link to full dashboard analysis

### 10.3 Deduplication Guard
A Redis key `apex_ai:alert_sent:{user_id}:{ticker}` with a **24-hour TTL** prevents flood alerts for the same signal within one day.

