## 12. FastAPI Backend ([main.py](file:///d:/AI-Stock-market-prediction-master/AI-Stock-market-prediction-master/main.py))

REST API exposing all ML modules for the React frontend and external consumers:

| Endpoint | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `GET /health` | Health check + model status |
| `POST /signal/{ticker}` | Run full inference → SignalOutput |
| `GET /screener` | Latest screener results from Redis |
| `GET /sentiment/{ticker}` | FinBERT sentiment for a ticker |
| `POST /backtest` | Run historical backtest |
| `GET /explainability/{ticker}` | SHAP feature importance |

Infrastructure: **CORS middleware**, **SlowAPI rate limiting**, request logging middleware, global exception handler, startup model-loading lifecycle.

