## 14. Security & Data Integrity

| Concern | Mitigation |
|---------|-----------|
| Data Leakage | **Causal padding** in all Conv1D layers; no future data in training |
| Outlier Sensitivity | **RobustScaler** for all feature normalization |
| Signal Quality | 3-gate system blocks low-confidence and high-uncertainty signals |
| Alert Flooding | 24-hour per-user-per-ticker Redis deduplication |
| Credentials | All secrets via **environment variables** (`.env` file, never hardcoded) |
| Stationarity | **Fractional Differentiation** (d=0.4) maintains long-memory while removing unit roots |

