## 16. Summary

Apex AI is a **research-grade, production-aware** stock trading intelligence system. Its core strength is the multi-layered pipeline that transforms raw market data → denoised, stationary features → probabilistic TFT forecasts → gated, explainable trading signals → actionable user notifications. The architecture is deliberately designed to avoid the two most common pitfalls in AI trading: lack of uncertainty quantification and absence of non-price (macro + sentiment) context.

> ⚠️ **Disclaimer:** This system is built for educational and research purposes. It is not financial advice. Always trade responsibly and understand the risks involved.
